hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: Children with disabilities colonialpillars.com Hated by many on the right for his extreme stance on environmental issues, he has become a poster boy of the green radical Left. However he enraged his fellow environmentalists when he was converted to the benefits of nuclear power. His opposition to capitalism and his insistence that Tony Blair is put on trial for crimes against peace have won him a dedicated following. Never knowingly uncontroversial, his books remain both popular and influential.
